	ly_dir_p

	* lily/music.cc (ly_get_mus_property): typechecking
	(ly_set_mus_property): idem
	(ly_make_music): idem
	(ly_music_name): idem

	* lily/chord.cc: use scm_reverse_x iso. gh_reverse()

